#circuitbreakersg day 47
It’s Vegetarian day 初一吃素. Had pineapple fried rice again but vegetarian this time! Not sure why but the rice was even tastier! Can taste the citrusy from the pineapple better 🤔🤔
Previous round we added prawns and chinese sausage, still good though. But I will definitely prefer vegetarian version for pineapple fried rice! (We use vegetarian ham for fried rice this time 🙏🏻) •
Bibik’s choice Jumbo vegetarian spring roll
Stir-fry beansprouts with Pea sprouts 
#stayhome #jxeatshome #vegetarian
Scrumptious! Haven’t had Thai food for so long 😋😋
That pineapple fried rice goes perfect with that spring roll 😍❤️
@yimmyadventures 😍😍 the pineapple add some points to presentation 😅
Omg the pineapple fried rice is soo cute!
Wow what a gourmet pineapple rice bowl ❤️
Omg that pineapple fried rice!!! I super love 😍
@ho4food thank you 😍 yes! the pineapple added points to presentation 😍
Looks so good! Always love the presentation of pineapple fried rice!
@the_chill_n_chew oh would love to see ur photo!! yess so delicious🤤
Made pineapple fried rice too. Best served in pineapple bowl 🙌🏽🙌🏽🙌🏽🙌🏽
